The paper discusses machine learning approaches for autonomous driving, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) techniques. The focus is on end-to-end approaches, which are related to artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (LG). The paper also discusses safety, which is related to systems and control (SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.RO, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
